channel.title: Prizo's House
channel.description:
Are you looking for those dirty electro beats fused with that classic house sound? Are you tired of looking all over for the perfect house mixx only to come up short listening to commercial dance tracks or trance music. Prizo's House contains the best in new and old House music from all over the world. All types of House music welcome mixed to perfection by yours truly. Have a track for submission? Send high quality mp3/wav files along with any info about the track.
Make sure you come to prizmatik.com and subscribe to mailing list and blog as well. Thanks and enjoy the music!

item.title: DJ PrizMatiK - Prizo's House Vol. 2
item.description: Welcome to the new podcast page for my newest syndicated mixshow: "Prizo's House". This is the second episode, freaked on Thanksgiving for your listening pleasure. I did not record a playlist for this one, so please do not ask. "Prizo's House" contains only the dopest House music around. From progressive to vocal to the classic joints you all remember. Syndicated on Mspot (Sprint / US Cellular mobile phones) and Digitally Imported (www.di.fm). Hope you enjoy. Hit me up direct with any feedback or other comments. PrizMatiK
